---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy | SaaS Pricing Toolkit"
  description="Privacy policy for this website and its analytics/ads integrations."
  robots="noindex,follow"
>
  <section class="hero">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p>
      This site provides calculators that run in your browser. We do not require accounts and we do not intentionally
      collect the inputs you enter into tools.
    </p>
  </section>

  <div class="grid">
    <section class="card col8">
      <h2>Advertising</h2>
      <p class="muted">
        If enabled by the site owner, we use Google AdSense to serve ads. Google and its partners may use cookies or
        similar technologies to personalize ads and measure performance.
      </p>
      <h2>Analytics</h2>
      <p class="muted">
        If enabled by the site owner, we use Google Analytics (GA4) to understand aggregated traffic and improve the site.
      </p>
      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p class="muted">
        Provide a contact email address here before launch.
      </p>
    </section>
    <aside class="card col4">
      <h2>Notes</h2>
      <p class="muted">
        Replace this page with your final policy and regional consent flow if you target jurisdictions that require it.
      </p>
    </aside>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
